EVENTS

private static final int[] EVENTS
The list of supported KiemEvent constants for this listener.

instance

private static KiemEventListener instance
The last created instance of the event listener.

Used to set the load/save imminent variables. This is done to prevent the listener from reporting events that were triggered by the plugin itself.

loadImminent

private boolean loadImminent
A plugin-triggered load is imminent, don't handle.
